@startuml AI Processing Pipeline Flow
!theme plain

title DaySave AI Processing Pipeline - Detailed Flow Chart\nFrom Content Creation to Analysis Completion

' Color definitions
!define START_COLOR #90EE90
!define PROCESS_COLOR #87CEEB
!define DECISION_COLOR #FFE4B5
!define AI_COLOR #DDA0DD
!define DATABASE_COLOR #98FB98
!define ERROR_COLOR #FFB6C1
!define END_COLOR #F0E68C

' Start
start
:User submits URL or uploads file;
note right: Content Routes Handler receives request

' Initial Processing
:Create Content record in database;
note right
    - Generate unique content ID
    - Store URL or file metadata
    - Set initial status
end note

:Initialize AutomationOrchestrator (Singleton);
note right: Get existing instance or create new one

if (Content Type?) then (URL)
    :UrlProcessor.isMultimediaUrl();
    note right: Check if URL contains multimedia content
    
    if (Is Multimedia URL?) then (yes)
        :UrlProcessor.detectPlatform();
        note right
            Detect platform:
            - YouTube
            - Instagram  
            - Facebook
            - TikTok
            - etc.
        end note
        
        :UrlProcessor.extractUrlMetadata();
        note right: Get basic metadata, thumbnails, title
        
        if (YouTube URL?) then (yes)
            :UrlProcessor.getYouTubeTranscription();
            note right
                Using yt-dlp:
                1. Extract captions (VTT format)
                2. Convert to plain text
                3. Fallback to audio download
            end note
        else (no)
            :Extract platform-specific metadata;
        endif
        
        :UrlProcessor.analyzeUrlContent();
        note right
            Comprehensive analysis:
            - Generate summary
            - Analyze sentiment  
            - Create auto-tags
            - Generate title
            - Speaker identification
        end note
        
    else (no)
        :Standard URL processing;
        note right: Non-multimedia content handling
    endif
    
else (File Upload)
    :AutomationOrchestrator.detectMediaType();
    note right
        Detection methods:
        - File extension analysis
        - MIME type checking
        - Buffer header analysis (magic numbers)
    end note
    
    :Select appropriate processor;
    note right
        Processor selection:
        - VideoProcessor for video files
        - AudioProcessor for audio files  
        - ImageProcessor for images
        - DocumentProcessor for documents
    end note
    
    :Initialize processor with configuration;
    note right: Load processor-specific settings and AI services
    
    :Validate file format and integrity;
    note right: Ensure file is valid and processable
    
    if (Media Type?) then (Video)
        partition "Video Processing Pipeline" #PROCESS_COLOR {
            :VideoProcessor.process();
            
            :Extract metadata (duration, resolution, codec);
            
            :Generate thumbnails at key frames;
            note right: Create multiple thumbnail sizes
            
            if (OCR Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Extract OCR captions from video frames;
                note right: Google Cloud Vision API
            endif
            
            if (Quality Analysis Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Analyze video quality metrics;
                note right: Resolution, clarity, encoding quality
            endif
            
            :Format video processing results;
        }
        
    elseif (Audio) then
        partition "Audio Processing Pipeline" #PROCESS_COLOR {
            :AudioProcessor.process();
            
            :Extract audio metadata;
            
            if (Transcription Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Transcribe audio to text;
                note right: Google Cloud Speech-to-Text API
            endif
            
            if (Speaker Diarization Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Identify different speakers;
                note right: Analyze voice patterns and segments
            endif
            
            if (Sentiment Analysis Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Analyze emotional content;
                note right: OpenAI GPT analysis
            endif
            
            :Format audio processing results;
        }
        
    elseif (Image) then
        partition "Image Processing Pipeline" #PROCESS_COLOR {
            :ImageProcessor.process();
            
            :Extract image metadata (dimensions, format);
            
            :Generate multiple thumbnail sizes;
            
            if (Object Detection Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Detect objects and entities;
                note right: Google Cloud Vision API
            endif
            
            if (OCR Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Extract text from image;
                note right: Google Cloud Vision OCR
            endif
            
            if (AI Description Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Generate AI description;
                note right: OpenAI GPT-4 Vision analysis
            endif
            
            if (Quality Analysis Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Analyze image quality;
                note right: Resolution, clarity, composition
            endif
            
            :Format image processing results;
        }
        
    else (Document)
        partition "Document Processing Pipeline" #PROCESS_COLOR {
            :DocumentProcessor.process();
            
            :Extract text content;
            note right: Support for PDF, DOC, TXT formats
            
            if (AI Analysis Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Generate AI summary;
                note right: OpenAI GPT analysis of content
            endif
            
            if (Tag Generation Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Generate auto-tags;
                note right: Extract key topics and themes
            endif
            
            if (Title Generation Enabled?) then (yes)
                :Generate descriptive title;
                note right: Create meaningful title from content
            endif
            
            :Format document processing results;
        }
    endif
endif

' AI Enhancement Phase
partition "AI Enhancement Phase" #AI_COLOR {
    if (Has transcription/text?) then (yes)
        :OpenAI GPT Analysis;
        note right
            AI-powered enhancements:
            - Summary generation
            - Sentiment analysis
            - Tag generation
            - Title improvement
            - Category classification
        end note
    endif
    
    :Combine all analysis results;
    note right: Merge processor results with AI enhancements
}

' Progress Tracking
partition "Progress Tracking" #PROCESS_COLOR {
    :ProgressTracker monitors all stages;
    note right
        Stage tracking:
        - Validation: 10%
        - Metadata extraction: 25%
        - Core processing: 50%
        - AI analysis: 75%
        - Finalization: 100%
    end note
    
    :ProgressWebSocketService broadcasts updates;
    note right: Real-time progress to frontend via WebSocket
}

' Performance Optimization
partition "Performance Optimization" #PROCESS_COLOR {
    :PerformanceOptimizer manages resources;
    note right
        Optimization features:
        - Memory usage monitoring
        - CPU load balancing
        - Queue management
        - Resource cleanup
    end note
    
    :PerformanceMonitor tracks metrics;
    note right: System health and performance alerts
}

' Database Storage
partition "Database Storage" #DATABASE_COLOR {
    :Format unified results;
    note right
        Standardized output:
        - jobId and mediaType
        - Processing time and metrics
        - Analysis results by type
        - Thumbnails and related data
    end note
    
    :Update Content record;
    note right
        Store in database:
        - transcription
        - summary  
        - generated_title
        - auto_tags
        - sentiment
        - metadata
    end note
    
    :Create related records;
    note right
        Additional tables:
        - Thumbnails
        - ProcessingJobs
        - VideoAnalysis/AudioAnalysis/ImageAnalysis
    end note
}

' Result Caching
if (Caching Enabled?) then (yes)
    :Cache results for future access;
    note right: Store in memory cache with expiration
endif

' Cleanup
:Cleanup temporary files and resources;
note right: Remove temp files, free memory, close connections

' Error Handling
floating note left: **Error Handling Throughout Pipeline:**\n• Retry mechanisms for failed operations\n• Graceful degradation when AI services unavailable\n• Comprehensive error logging\n• Progress tracking continues on partial failures\n• User feedback on processing status

' Completion
:Analysis complete;
note right
    Final status:
    - Success/failure indication
    - Processing time metrics
    - Analysis results summary
    - User notification ready
end note

stop

' Performance Notes
floating note right: **Performance Features:**\n• Singleton pattern prevents multiple orchestrator instances\n• Async processing with progress tracking\n• Memory-efficient streaming for large files\n• Result caching reduces repeated processing\n• Queue management prevents system overload\n• Automatic cleanup prevents resource leaks

' Architecture Notes  
floating note left: **Key Architecture Benefits:**\n• Modular processor design allows easy extension\n• Plugin registry enables feature toggles\n• Configuration manager centralizes settings\n• Progress tracking provides user feedback\n• Error recovery maintains system stability\n• Performance monitoring ensures reliability

@enduml
